# {{COMPONENT_TITLE}}

Use this component skill together with `shemic-dever`. Read `shemic-dever` first for framework rules, then apply the component-specific rules here.

## Source Of Truth

- Component source: `package/{{COMPONENT_NAME}}`
- Component pages: `package/{{COMPONENT_NAME}}/front/page`
- Component front plugin: `package/{{COMPONENT_NAME}}/front/src/plugin.ts`
- Component metadata: `package/{{COMPONENT_NAME}}/dever.json`

## Rules

- Reuse package/front page JSON capabilities before writing Service/API.
- Do not create CRUD wrapper Service/API.
- Do not edit generated files or compiled front assets.
- Keep component-specific behavior inside this component.
- Document any public API, permission, or migration behavior here.

## Common Checks

- Read existing models before changing page JSON.
- Read existing services before adding new Provider/API.
- Check component permissions before changing admin pages.
